com.sap.spe.pricing.customizing

Class PricingCustomizingConstants.ConditionSubtotal

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.spe.pricing.customizing.PricingCustomizingConstants.ConditionSubtotal
  • Enclosing class:
    PricingCustomizingConstants

    public static final class PricingCustomizingConstants.ConditionSubtotal
extends java.lang.Object
    Controls whether and in which fields condition amounts or subtotals (for example, a customer discount or the cost of a material) are stored.
    See Also:
    IPricingStep
